\documentclass[border=2mm]{standalone}
\usepackage{tikz}

\begin{document}

\begin{tikzpicture}

% \draw (0, 0) grid (2, 2);
% \draw (0, 0) grid [xstep=.75cm, ystep=1cm] (3, 3);
\draw[help lines, red] (0, 0) grid [step=.75cm, rotate=45] (3, 3);

\end{tikzpicture}

\end{document}


网格的画法：起点(0, 0)，画网格grid命令，对角重点(2, 2). x[0, 2] y[0, 2]
